<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n11130d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n11" href="#n11130d">N11 (VI.B.5)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n11all.htm#n11130d"> 130(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font face="wake">D</font> takes off his coat,</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">A l&apos;offertoire, <mark>le pr&ecirc;tre se d&eacute;pouilla des ses ornements</mark>, ne conserva qu&apos;une tunique de lin, &hellip; Ma soeur profite de mon trouble; elle avance hardiment la t&ecirc;te. Sa superbe chevelure tombe de toutes parts sous le fer sacr&eacute;; <br><font color="green">[At the Offertory, the priest stripped off his ornaments, kept only a linen tunic, ... My sister takes advantage of my trouble; she boldly advances her head. Her superb hair falls on all sides under the sacred iron;]</font> <small> Chateaubriand, <a name="CHBD" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CHBD"><cite title="source">&OElig;uvres choisies illustr&eacute;es</cite></a> (1912) I, <i>Ren&eacute;</i> 102</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
